@startuml
!include ../../../images/common-sequence.iuml

title Client Provisioning — Controller SoftAP Flow

actor User

box "Client Device\n(ESP8266)"
    participant "Client\nFirmware" as Client
end box

box "Controller (ESP32)"
    participant "SoftAP\n(SSID: FireFly-Provisioning)" as AP
    participant "HTTP API" as API
end box

User -> API++ : **Enable Provisioning Mode**\nPUT /api/provisioning\n""{visual-token}""

break visual-token Invalid
    API --> User : HTTP 401
end

API --> User : HTTP 202
API -> AP-- : **Start SoftAP**\nWPA2 password = ""nibble-interleave(BSSID)""\nTX power = ""2 dBm""\nmax clients = ""1""


Client -> Client : **Scan for SSID**\n"""FireFly-Provisioning""" (exact)
Client -> Client : **Read BSSID from scan result**\ncompute password = ""nibble-interleave(BSSID)""
Client -> Client : **Reduce TX power to minimum**
Client -> AP++ : **Connect using WPA2**\nwith computed password
AP -> AP : **Verify MAC in allowlist**

break MAC not in allowlist
    AP -> API : **Rogue client event**
    API -> API : **Mark MAC Address as Rogue Client**
    API -> AP : **Shut down SoftAP**
    AP --> Client-- : Disconnect
end

AP --> Client-- : Connected (DHCP 192.168.4.x)

Client -> API++ : **Get nonce**\nGET /api/provisioning/nonce

break Request is not from SoftAP
    API --> Client: HTTP 403
end

API --> Client-- : HTTP 200\n""{ "nonce": 3819273645 }""

Client -> API++ : **Get client payload from its MAC Address**\nGET /api/provisioning/client\n""mac-address: aa:bb:cc:dd:ee:ff""\n""x-nonce: 3819273645"""

break Request is not from SoftAP
    API --> Client: HTTP 403
end

API -> API : **Validate nonce**\nunused, matches session

break Nonce used or invalid
    API --> Client: HTTP 401
end

API -> API : **Find client record by ""mac-address""**

break No client with ""mac-address""
    API --> Client: HTTP 404
end

API -> API : **Invalidate nonce**
API --> Client-- : HTTP 200\n""{client}""

Client -> Client : **Store config to LittleFS**
Client -> Client : **Reboot into normal mode**

User -> API++ : **Disable Provisioning Mode**\nDELETE /api/provisioning\n""{visual-token}""
API --> User : HTTP 202
API -> AP-- : **Shut down SoftAP**

@enduml